{"tid":2199540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援12手足 懇請民陣/集會團隊入紙大遊行","createTime":"2020-09-12T09:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T19:20:24.000Z","uid":114951,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"135b32cfff2a4e7cd613b03d35f8ddd36b565307","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:31:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">TLDR: 要向港共中国施壓/引起國際廣泛討論，就要用返最原始嘅方法<br />\n大。遊。行。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n初步咁諗有兩個原因<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n最主要同最直接嘅原因<br />\n就係而家政府冷處理12手足被捕<br />\n就算喺香港社會入邊都冇引起好廣泛嘅討論<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">需要以遊行帶起關注熱度</span></span><br />\n可能大家會覺得上升到國際層面自己幫唔到咩手<br />\n<span class=\"red\">但係其實聲援遊行已經係比緊家屬同手足最大嘅支持</span><br />\n而且要留意嘅係<br />\n<span class=\"red\">手足連最基本法律嘅權利都冇<br />\n喺監獄入邊疑似被剃光頭<br />\n甚至受到酷刑</span><br />\n(Source: 蘋果)<br />\n要令到手足得到最基本嘅法律保障<br />\n起碼可以遣返返嚟香港先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">所以更加要以遊行反映關注熱度<br />\n引起國際討論</span><br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n其實呢次亦都係機會<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">等我哋可以connect牆內維權律師/維權人士</span></span><br />\n最近本土思潮崛起<br />\n令到好多人對中国嘅所有嘢都覺得好反感<br />\n但係其實牆內都有好多人有唔同聲音默默咁努力緊<br />\n好似蓬佩奧所講<br />\n要改變中共就需要中国人民嘅努力<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/蓬佩奧呼籲中國人民改變中共-與華盲目交往舊模式失敗/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1-%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%B2%E7%9B%AE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80%E8%88%8A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b85806ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1-%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%B2%E7%9B%AE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80%E8%88%8A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%2F&h=8d28958c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/蓬佩奧呼籲中國人民改變中共-與華盲目交往舊模式失敗/</a>)<br />\n今次事件亦係好好嘅機會反映中国所謂「陽光司法」根本係垃圾<br />\nConnect埋牆內手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而大遊行就可以將呢件事擺上枱面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他意見歡迎提出<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">撐手足<br />\n撐到底<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n呢啲唔單止係口號<br />\n係要用行動證明出黎</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">利申番先<br />\n樓主唔建議大家做任何犯法野<br />\nMon po狗唔好諗住周鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fefd05c931dd76f3ddb2bf18ddba2fc1e4a22fd7","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">撐手足<br />\n撐到底</span></span>"},{"pid":"3263c3a3c6654c635874ce4313188c90902f1600","tid":2199540,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ecce68a3ad32834fb3c027e5e880dc3aa35290","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"size=6]<span class=\"red\">撐手足<br />\n撐到底</span>[/size=6]"},{"pid":"88bcea3738593664d2635a831b0bd3a1d6c9157d","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span clas