ees in need<br />\n<br />\n3. Allow the detainees to call their families<br />\n<br />\n4. Potect human rights of the detainee and send them back to Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n#save12<br />\n#save12hkyouths<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以share同twitter 出去"},{"pid":"c5ce66acc39c0bfdcdc47f828a81c329452f6fc1","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:38:56.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"3eb710f37051c8e9574615eac1c5ab714c76d3c4","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0723d3f387813a544bbb7155f1e42d72c9a1bca5","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"推牙"},{"pid":"caeaa0a3578fb0f16b6c1c9bce61571dfab6d869","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"2c560201384318127242f59ba70e9bc04fce4fbd","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"撐手足"},{"pid":"1f35ef530b90f7d3180bed48a1a0d5e95039eb50","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"撐到底"},{"pid":"e3853bf98993621f402ceb025be49c4d5cfa4332","tid":2199540,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"十一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都要遊行俾家屬俾國際社會知<br />\n我們無放棄佢地"},{"pid":"8c7c5f6148348313b73e7a84b1e886d159fb5827","tid":2199540,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/